      <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto md:py-16 p-8 text-center">
        <h1 class="text-white text-6xl font-bold mb-16">Confuse, Code, Repeat!</h1>
        <div class="md:flex md:justify-center space-y-8 md:space-y-0 md:gap-x-8 dark:text-white">
          <div>
            <div class="bg-zinc-100 dark:bg-zinc-900 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-xl">
              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">Baby Steps</h2>
              <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 my-4">
                Ready to scratch your head? Let's get started with the basics of Confuscript. Learn how to install and write your first program.
              </p>
              <a href="/docs/get-started/introduction" class="inline-block bg-green-700 hover:bg-green-800 text-white text-lg font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded">
                LEARN
