              <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold">Getting Confused? Let’s Start!</h2>
              <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 my-4">
                Dive headfirst into the wonderful chaos!
                Instructions, or rather, de-structions on how to code in this confusing language.
              </p>
              <a href="/docs/documentation/introduction" class="inline-block bg-blue-700 hover:bg-blue-800 text-white text-lg font-bold py-2 px-4 rounded">
                DOCUMENTATION
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div>
            <div class="bg-zinc-100 dark:bg-zinc-900 p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-xl">
