          Predicting the future of Confuscript? I have no idea. It surely was fun! I hope you have fun too!
        </p>
      </div>
      <a href="/docs/get-started/introduction" class="w-fit px-8 my-4 text-center mx-auto block bg-blue-700 hover:bg-bluee-800 text-white text-lg font-bold py-2 rounded">
        Get Started
      </a>
    </div>
	</main>
</Layout>
